sourcesContent:
export const list = [
{
	id: 1,
	name: 'React',
	image: require('./images/tiles/react.png'),
	image1: require('./images/video/end.jpeg'),
	description: "After the devastating events of Avengers: Infinity War (2018), the universe is in ruins. With the help of remaining allies, the Avengers assemble once more in order to reverse Thanos' actions and restore balance to the universe."
},
{
	id: 2,
	name: 'Vue.js',
	image: require('./images/tiles/captain_marvel.jpg'),
	image1: require('./images/video/cap_marvel.jpg'),
	description: "Carol Danvers becomes one of the universe's most powerful heroes when Earth is caught in the middle of a galactic war between two alien races."
},
{
	id:3,
	name: 'Angular',
	image: require('./images/tiles/shazam.jpg'),
	image1: require('./images/video/shazam.jpeg'),
	description: "We all have a superhero inside us, it just takes a bit of magic to bring it out. In Billy Batson's case, by shouting out one word - SHAZAM - this streetwise fourteen-year-old foster kid can turn into the grown-up superhero Shazam."
},
{
	id:4,
	name: 'Express',
	image: require('./images/tiles/infinity_wars.jpg'),
	image1: require('./images/video/infinity_wars.jpg'),
	description: "The Avengers and their allies must be willing to sacrifice all in an attempt to defeat the powerful Thanos before his blitz of devastation and ruin puts an end to the universe."

},
{
	id:5,
	name: 'Next.js',
	image: require('./images/tiles/got.jpg'),
	image1: require('./images/video/s8e02.jpg'),
	description: "Nine noble families fight for control over the mythical lands of Westeros, while an ancient enemy returns after being dormant for thousands of years."

},
{
	id:6,
	name: 'Most Used',
	image: require('./images/tiles/flash.jpg'),
	image1: require('./images/video/flash.jpg'),
	description: "After being struck by lightning, Barry Allen wakes up from his coma to discover he's been given the power of super speed, becoming the Flash, fighting crime in Central City."

},
{
	id:7,
	name: 'Highest Interest',
	image: require('./images/tiles/blindspot.jpg'),
	image1: require('./images/video/blindspot.jpg'),
	description: "Jane Doe is found in Times Square with no memory and mysterious tattoos on her body."

},
{
	id:8,
	name: 'Highest Satisfaction',
	image: require('./images/tiles/walking_dead.jpg'),
	image1: require('./images/video/dead.jpg'),
	description: "Sheriff Deputy Rick Grimes wakes up from a coma to learn the world is in ruins, and must lead a group of survivors to stay alive."
}
]
